'''Drop nets''' were seemingly primative weapons used in a variety of advanced vehicles. Most notably, the [[64-Y Swift 3 Repulsorlift Sled|64-Y Swift 3 repulsor sleds]] used by the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Empire]] were equipped with drop nets.

